@startuml
title Iterator

skinparam legendBackgroundColor #f9f9f9
skinparam legendBorderColor #999999

legend right
**Intent**: Provide sequential access to elements without exposing representation.

**Use when**: Collections wish to offer uniform traversal.

**Key participants**: Iterator, ConcreteIterator, Aggregate, ConcreteAggregate.
endlegend

interface Iterator {
  +hasNext() : boolean
  +next() : Element
}

interface Aggregate {
  +createIterator() : Iterator
}

class ConcreteIterator
class ConcreteAggregate

Iterator <|.. ConcreteIterator
Aggregate <|.. ConcreteAggregate
ConcreteAggregate o-- ConcreteIterator : creates
@enduml